Hangman Game 🎮
📌 Overview
The Hangman Game is a classic word-guessing game where the player tries to guess a hidden word by suggesting letters within a limited number of attempts. If the player fails to guess the word before the chances run out, they lose the game.

🔹 Features
✅ Command-line interface for an interactive experience
✅ Random word selection for each game session
✅ Tracks incorrect guesses and displays remaining attempts
✅ Hints to help players when stuck
✅ Simple and beginner-friendly Python implementation

⚙️ How to Run
Clone this repository:
bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/praneethramisetti168/HANGMAN-GAME.git
