🛠 Technologies Used
Python
Random module for word selection
📌 How to Play
The game selects a random word and displays blank spaces (_) for each letter.
The player enters a letter guess.
The letter appears in the correct position if it is in the word.
If the guess is wrong, the player loses an attempt.
The game continues until:
The player correctly guesses the word (Win 🎉)
The player runs out of attempts (Lose 💀)



